OL,3,CFraudster took #75k from dad left
OL,4,Cbrain damaged after crash
OL,6,FA woman defrauded her "highly
OL,7,Fvulnerable" father out of almost
OL,8,F#75,000 after he suffered serious
OL,9,Fbrain damage in a crash.
OL,11,FTamara Whiting, from Hull, made cash
OL,12,Fwithdrawals from her father's account,
OL,13,Fbought goods on Amazon and paid off
OL,14,Fcredit card bills.
OL,16,FHull Crown Court heard it was a "clear
OL,17,Fabuse of power" against her father
OL,18,Fcarried out over a "sustained period
OL,19,Fof time".
