OL,4,Cbrain damaged after crash
OL,6,FAshleigh Metcalfe, prosecuting, said
OL,7,FWhiting's father suffered brain
OL,8,Finjuries in a road accident in 1995
OL,9,Fand his mental capacity was severely
OL,10,Fimpaired.
OL,12,FHe was awarded #180,000 in
OL,13,Fcompensation following the crash.
OL,14,FAfter he separated from his wife,
OL,15,FWhiting was appointed as his receiver.
OL,17,FAfter her father died in June 2022 at
OL,18,Fthe age of 71, Whiting was found to
OL,19,Fhave fraudulently obtained #74,580,
OL,20,Fmost of it being cash withdrawals.
